'''笑死'''是一種罕見的死因，通常是由人類一陣大笑而引起的[[心臟驟停|心臟驟停]]或者[[窒息|窒息]]導致的死亡，因此非常危險。自[[古希臘|古希臘]]時代至現代均有笑死的案例紀錄。笑死的別稱「致命的歡鬧」（{{lang-en|fatal hilarity}}）則是於1956年首次被使用<ref>Oxford: Clarendon Press (1993). The Compact Oxford English Dictionary.</ref>。

== 病理生理 ==
大笑不只可以引致[[心臟驟停|心臟驟停]]或[[窒息|窒息]]。<ref name="pmid18493621">{{cite journal |author=Reiss AL, Hoeft F, Tenforde AS, Chen W, Mobbs D, Mignot EJ |title=Anomalous hypothalamic responses to humor in cataplexy |journal=PLoS ONE |volume=3 |issue=5 |pages=e2225 |year=2008 |pmid=18493621 |pmc=2377337 |doi=10.1371/journal.pone.0002225 |url=http://www.plosone.org/article/info:doi/10.1371/journal.pone.0002225 |editor1-last=Greene |editor1-first=Ernest}}</ref>笑亦可以引致[[收縮乏力|收縮乏力]]、[[虛脫|虛脫]]和[[昏厥|昏厥]]<ref name="pmid18538031">{{cite journal |author=Nishida K, Hirota SK, Tokeshi J |title=Laugh syncope as a rare sub-type of the situational syncopes: a case report |journal=J Med Case Reports |volume=2 |issue= 1|page=197 |year=2008 |pmid=18538031 |pmc=2440757 |doi=10.1186/1752-1947-2-197 |url=http://www.jmedicalcasereports.com/content/2/1/197}}</ref><ref name="pmid14592259">{{cite journal |author=Totah AR, Benbadis SR |title=Gelastic syncope mistaken for cataplexy |journal=Sleep Med. |volume=3 |issue=1 |pages=77–8 |pmid=14592259 |doi= 10.1016/S1389-9457(01)00113-7|url=http://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S1389945701001137|date=January 2002}}</ref>，並會導致[[創傷|創傷]]。<ref name="pmid17976409">{{cite journal |author=Lo R, Cohen TJ |title=Laughter-induced syncope: no laughing matter |journal=Am. J. Med. |volume=120 |issue=11 |pages=e5 |pmid=17976409 |doi=10.1016/j.amjmed.2006.07.019 |url=http://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0002-9343(06)00898-9 |date=November 2007 |access-date=2013-05-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181004021227/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0002-9343(06)00898-9 |archive-date=2018-10-04 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>因笑昏厥可能因下丘腦局灶性病變所致。<ref name="pmid18077234">{{cite journal |author=Cheung CS, Parrent AG, Burneo JG |title=Gelastic seizures: not always hypothalamic hamartoma |journal=Epileptic Disord |volume=9 |issue=4 |pages=453–8 |pmid=18077234 |doi=10.1684/epd.2007.0139 |url=http://www.john-libbey-eurotext.fr/en/revues/medecine/epd/e-docs/00/04/37/CC/article.phtml|date=December 2007}}</ref>因笑昏厥亦會影響[[小腦|小腦]]。<ref name="pmid17662020">{{cite journal |author=Famularo G, Corsi FM, Minisola G, De Simone C, Nicotra GC |title=Cerebellar tumour presenting with pathological laughter and gelastic syncope |journal=Eur. J. Neurol. |volume=14 |issue=8 |pages=940–3 |pmid=17662020 |doi=10.1111/j.1468-1331.2007.01784.x |url=http://www.blackwell-synergy.com/openurl?genre=article&sid=nlm:pubmed&issn=1351-5101&date=2007&volume=14&issue=8&spage=940 |date=August 2007 }}{{dead link|date=2018年1月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>

笑可以是一種病症。[[橋腦|橋腦]]或[[延髓|延髓]]的梗塞均可以引致病者大笑，繼而死去。以這種方式死亡的病者可能被誤以為是因大笑而死。<ref name="Gondim">{{cite journal | last=Gondim | first=FA | coauthors=Parks BJ, Cruz-Flores S et al. | title="Fou rire prodromique" as the presentation of pontine ischaemia secondary to vertebrobasilar stenosis | url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-neurology-neurosurgery-and-psychiatry_2001-12_71_6/page/802 | journal=Journal of Neurology, Neurosurgery, and Psychiatry | volume=71 | issue=6 | pages=802–804 | date=December 2001 | pmid=11723208 | pmc=1737630 | doi=10.1136/jnnp.71.6.802 }}</ref>

== 歷史上笑死的案例 ==
歷史上曾經有少量笑死案例，可追溯至公元前5世紀的古希臘。於近代，笑死的人主要都是因笑引致的心臟衰竭或窒息而死。<ref name="snopes"/>
*公元前5世紀的古希臘畫家[[宙克西斯|宙克西斯]]：他在繪畫一位[[滑稽|滑稽]]的老女人時笑死。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://oxfordindex.oup.com/view/10.1093/oi/authority.20110803133443737|title=OVERVIEW Zeuxis|publisher=Oxford Index|accessdate=2013-05-11}}</ref>
*公元前3世紀的古希臘[[斯多葛派|斯多葛派]]哲學家[[克律西波斯|克律西波斯]]：他的其中一個死亡說法指出當他看見一隻[[驢子|驢子]]正在吃[[無花果|無花果]]，便命令奴隸給那隻驢子酒喝。之後，他大笑而死。<ref name="Chrysippus">{{cite book|first=Diogenes|last= Laertius|title=Lives, Teachings and Sayings of the Eminent Philosophers, with an English translation by R.D. Hicks|year=1964-5|publisher=Harvard UP/W. Heinemann Ltd|location=Cambridge, Mass/London}}</ref>
*統治者[[马丁一世_(阿拉贡)|马丁一世]]：他於1410年因[[消化不良|消化不良]]和無法控制的痴笑而死。<ref>Paul N. Morris, ''[https://web.archive.org/web/20060304124353/http://www.cc.jyu.fi/mirator/pdf/Morris.pdf Patronage and Piety Montserrat and the Royal House of Medieval Catalonia-Aragon]'', October 2000</ref>
*[[文藝復興時期|文藝復興時期]]意大利作家[[彼得罗·阿雷蒂诺|彼得罗·阿雷蒂诺]]：他於1556年因大笑不止引致的窒息而死。<ref>Waterfield, Gordon, ed. ''First Footsteps in East Africa'', (New York: Praeger Publishers, 1966) pg. 59 footnote.</ref>
*[[蘇格蘭|蘇格蘭]]作家和翻譯[[托馬斯·厄克特|托馬斯·厄克特]]：他於1660年在聽聞[[查理二世_(英格蘭)|查理二世]]登基後笑死。<ref>{{cite book | title = Rabelais in English Literature | last = Brown | first = Huntington | isbn = 0-7146-2051-3 | publisher = Routledge | page = 126 | year = 1968}}</ref><ref>{{cite book | title = The History of Scottish Poetry | url = https://archive.org/details/historyscotishp00irvigoog | publisher = Edmonston & Douglas | year = 1861 | page = [https://archive.org/details/historyscotishp00irvigoog/page/n576 539]}}</ref>
*英格蘭金斯林的亞歷克斯·米切爾：他於1975年3月24日在觀看《功夫Kapers》時，看到了一位帶著[[風笛|風笛]]的蘇格蘭人與一位帶著[[血腸|血腸]]的蘭開斯特門派大師決鬥。<ref name="snopes">{{cite web | url = http://www.snopes.com/horrors/freakish/laughing.asp | title = The Last Laugh's on Him | work = Urban Legends Reference Pages | date = 2007-01-19 | accessdate = 2007-06-23}}</ref>之後，他不斷大笑，並在連續笑了25分鐘後突然[[心臟衰竭|心臟衰竭]]而死。<ref>''The Complete Goodies'' — Robert Ross, B T Batsford, London, 2000.</ref><ref>''Man Dies Laughing at The Goodies'', "Daily Mail", London (29 March 1975)</ref>他的遺孀隨後致函予《功夫Kapers》製作組，以感謝他們在丈夫臨死前給予他歡樂。<ref>''A Goodies Way to Go — Laughing'', "Eastern Daily Press", Norwich (29 March 1975)</ref><ref>''Slapstick! The Illustrated Story of Knockabout Comedy'' — Tony Staveacre, Angus & Robinson 1987</ref>
*[[丹麥|丹麥]][[聽力師|聽力師]]奧萊·本特森：他於1989年在觀看《[[一條叫旺達的魚|-{zh-tw:笨賊一籮筐; zh-hk:靚女大賊神仙魚; zh-cn:一条叫旺达的鱼;}-]]》時不停大笑而死。據驗屍官估計，本特森的心臟在心臟驟停前的心跳速度為[[心跳过速|每分鐘250至500次心跳]]。<ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20080412072030/http://www.canongate.net/Lists/Death/9PeopleWhoDiedLaughing 9 People Who Died Laughing - Death - Book of Lists - Canongate Home]</ref>
*[[泰國|泰國]]冰淇淋推銷員丹能·肖恩：他於2003年在睡眠期間笑死。當時，他的妻子無法叫醒他。兩分鐘後，他便停止了呼吸。他的死因很可能是心臟衰竭或窒息。<ref name="snopes"/>

==文艺作品情節==
在《[[三国演义|三国演义]]》故事中，[[司马昭|司马昭]]在酒宴席间因为[[刘禅|刘禅]]“乐不思蜀”言词反覆的对话哈哈大笑，而在1994年播映的[[三国演义_(电视剧)|电视剧《三国演义》]]，劇情被改编为司马昭在現場笑死了自己。

在小说《[[薛刚反唐|薛刚反唐]]》第九十六回“双孝王大开铁坟　[[樊梨花|樊梨花]]回山修道”中，128岁高龄的[[程咬金|程咬金]]在祭奠被害的薛家家眷时，回顾自己一生的经历，感叹“真如做了一百二十八岁的春梦”，最后大笑而逝。

小说《[[说岳全传|说岳全传]]》第七十九回“施岑收服乌灵圣母　[[牛皋|牛皋]]气死完颜兀术”中，牛皋生擒了金国统帅[[完颜兀术|完颜兀术]]，并骑在兀术背上对其羞辱，兀术当场被气得吐血而死。牛皋哈哈大笑，最后“一口气不接，竟笑死于兀术身上”。

